r\n3. 四盘位，不需要阵列；\r\n\r\n先行谢过了。", "content_rendered": "<p>需要在 NUC 上外接一个硬盘盒做 NAS 。在京东搜了半天，几乎只有奥睿科的，但是听说奥睿科硬盘盒不稳定？</p>\n<p>需求：</p>\n<ol>\n<li>自带风扇，散热良好；</li>\n<li>USB3.0 以上</li>\n<li>四盘位，不需要阵列；</li>\n</ol>\n<p>先行谢过了。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1635582735, "replies": 25, "id": 811753}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_large.png?m=1608969785", "name": "life", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_normal.png?m=1608969785", "title": "生活", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/life", "topics": 2663, "footer": "", "header": "生活中的技术讨论", "title_alternative": "Life", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6e27/13a6/557_mini.png?m=1608969785", "stars": 682, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 557, "parent_node_name": ""}, "member": {"username": "Danswerme", "website": "", "github": "", "psn": "", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/7460/e1cd/274090_mini.png?m=1635160674", "bio": "", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/Danswerme", "tagline": "", "twitter": "", "created": 1513081062, "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/7460/e1cd/274090_mini.png?m=1635160674", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/7460/e1cd/274090_mini.png?m=1635160674", "location": "", "btc": "", "id": 274090}, "last_reply_by": "Danswerme", "last_touched": 1635609425, "title": "瞌睡越来越多了", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/811698", "created": 1635564481, "deleted": 0, "content": "一般都是晚上 11 点左右睡觉，最迟不超过 12 点，早上 7 点闹钟响。\r\n\r\n不知道什么时候开始，早上被闹钟吵醒时变的很困，大脑一片混沌根本起不来，都是被按时上班的责任感给硬生生催起来的，起来洗把脸后就好多了。\r\n\r\n最近离职了，早上没有闹钟等自然醒的时候就已经 10 点多了；今天更离谱，醒来已经 11 点了，还是困的要命，怀疑是不是身体出了什么问题。", "content_rendered": "<p>一般都是晚上 11 点左右睡觉，最迟不超过 12 点，早上 7 点闹钟响。</p>\n<p>不知道什么时候开始，早上被闹钟吵醒时变的很困，大脑一片混沌根本起不来，都是被按时上班的责任感给硬生生催起来的，起来洗把脸后就好多了。</p>\n<p>最近离职了，早上没有闹钟等自然醒的时候就已经 10 点多了；今天更离谱，醒来已经 11 点了，还是困的要命，怀疑是不是身体出了什么问题。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1635564511, "replies": 24, "id": 811698}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_large.png?m=1630643913", "name": "apple", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_normal.png?m=1630643913", "title": "Apple", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/apple", "topics": 16577, "footer": "", "header": "设计了 <a href=\"/go/watch\">Apple Watch</a>，<a href=\"/go/ipad\">iPad</a>，<a href=\"/go/iphone\">iPhone</a>，<a href=\"/go/imac\">iMac</a> 及 <a href=\"/go/mbp\">MacBook Pro</a> 等电子产品的美国公司。", "title_alternative": "Apple", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_mini.png?m=1630643913", "stars": 1980, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 184, "parent_node_name": "hardware"}, "member": {"username": "duxiansen", "website": "", "github": "", "psn": "", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/6353/3531/193937_mini.png?m=1635571394", "bio": "", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/duxiansen", "tagline": "", "twitter": "", "created": 1475070422, "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/6353/3531/193937_mini.png?m=1635571394", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/6353/3531/193937_mini.png?m=1635571394", "location": "", "btc": "", "id": 193937}, "last_reply_by": "nolan1864", "last_touched": 1635602667, "title": "用 SwitchResX 选择一个 16:10 的分辨率，就可以完全屏蔽刘海儿了", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/811724", "created": 1635571503, "deleted": 0, "content": "转自微博 @BugOS 技术组\r\n\r\n有到手的可以自己测一下，效果应该是和正常屏幕一样了\r\n\r\n如果可以的话，算是比较理想的方法解决了讨厌刘海的那部分人的需求吧", "content_rendered": "<p>转自微博 @<a href=\"/member/BugOS\">BugOS</a> 技术组</p>\n<p>有到手的可以自己测一下，效果应该是和正常屏幕一样了</p>\n<p>如果可以的话，算是比较理想的方法解决了讨厌刘海的那部分人的需求吧</p>\n", "last_modified": 1635571503, "replies": 23, "id": 811724}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_large.png?m=1630643913", "name": "apple", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_normal.png?m=1630643913", "title": "Apple", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/apple", "topics": 16577, "footer": "", "header": "设计了 <a href=\"/go/watch\">Apple Watch</a>，<a href=\"/go/ipad\">iPad</a>，<a href=\"/go/iphone\">iPhone</a>，<a href=\"/go/imac\">iMac</a> 及 <a href=\"/go/mbp\">MacBook Pro</a> 等电子产品的美国公司。", "title_alternative": "Apple", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_mini.png?m=1630643913", "stars": 1980, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 184, "parent_node_name": "hardware"}, "member": {"username": "milkleeeeee", "website": "", "github": "lmk123", "psn": "", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/b2fa71489dab8156df166c16ec51f54b?s=24&d=retro", "bio": "", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/milkleeeeee", "tagline": "", "twitter": "", "created": 1425548795, "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/b2fa71489dab8156df166c16ec51f54b?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/b2fa71489dab8156df166c16ec51f54b?s=24&d=retro", "location": "", "btc": "", "id": 102641}, "last_reply_by": "njzy", "last_touched": 1635609271, "title": "升级 Monterey 之后电脑变卡了", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/811744", "created": 1635580335, "deleted": 0, "content": "升级之前都好好的，升级之后可以明显感觉到卡顿，即使在刚开机没有开启任何程序的情况下也会经常出现以下问题：\r\n\r\n- 拖动鼠标时，鼠标指针会先在原位停留大概 0.3 秒，然后才瞬间移动到新的位置\r\n- 打开一个网页后，滚动网页时，网页会停留大概 0.3 秒，然后才瞬间滚动到新的位置\r\n- 用触控板单击时，偶尔会没点成功，需要再点一次\r\n\r\n这些问题在升级前都是没有的，所以应该不是电脑配置的问题？（我的是 M1 Air 16g ）\r\n\r\n有跟我一样有这些问题的人吗", "content_rendered": "<p>升级之前都好好的，升级之后可以明显感觉到卡顿，即使在刚开机没有开启任何程序的情况下也会经常出现以下问题：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>拖动鼠标时，鼠标指针会先在原位停留大概 0.3 秒，然后才瞬间移动到新的位置</li>\n<li>打开一个网页后，滚动网页时，网页会停留大概 0.3 秒，然后才瞬间滚动到新的位置</li>\n<li>用触控板单击时，偶尔会没点成功，需要再点一次</li>\n</ul>\n<p>这些问题在升级前都是没有的，所以应该不是电脑配置的问题？（我的是 M1 Air 16g ）</p>\n<p>有跟我一样有这些问题的人吗</p>\n", "last_modified": 1635580335, "replies": 22, "id": 811744}]